Dudley is one of my top choices to go to in LA! They catch their own fish, they have a great selection of wine and the staff is super nice. You can also buy their sustainable fresh caught fish to cook at home. Always a solid choice.

Dudley Market isn't only a front runner in food, they also know how to make you feel comfortable and like family. Their wine selection is fantastic and they know how to pair it perfectly with whatever fresh catch they're serving that day. I can't say better things about Dudley, their fare and their staff!
